text: This is an Indian grocery store. All sorts of vegetables, Indian grocery are available. Evenings you can get fresh vegetables and is a bit crowded than usual times. Also, there is a playground opposite to the store. You can leave your kids and do your purchases. Prices are a bit costly it seems.
